{"text_id":117992,"tokens":["The"," D",".","C","."," Opportunity"," Scholarship"," Program"," (","OSP",")"," is"," a"," private"," school"," voucher"," program"," in"," Washington",","," D",".","C",".,"," established"," by"," the"," U",".","S","."," Congress"," in"," ","2","0","0","4","."," The"," program"," provides"," scholarships"," to"," low","-","income"," families"," in"," the"," District"," of"," Columbia"," to"," help"," them"," send"," their"," children"," to"," participating"," private"," schools","."," The"," OSP"," is"," the"," only"," federally"," funded"," voucher"," program"," in"," the"," United"," States",".","\n\n","The"," program"," was"," created"," as"," a"," pilot"," initiative",","," with"," funding"," for"," ","1",",","7","0","0"," scholarships",","," as"," part"," of"," the"," Consolidated"," Appropriations"," Act"," of"," ","2","0","0","4","."," The"," program"," was"," re","authorized"," in"," ","2","0","1","1"," through"," the"," Scholarships"," for"," Opportunity"," and"," Results"," Act"," (","SO","AR",")."," The"," SO","AR"," Act"," extended"," the"," program"," through"," ","2","0","1","6",","," and"," removed"," the"," cap"," on"," the"," number"," of"," scholarships"," that"," could"," be"," awarded","."," In"," ","2","0","1","7",","," the"," program"," was"," again"," re","authorized"," through"," the"," Consolidated"," Appropriations"," Act",","," which"," funded"," the"," program"," through"," the"," ","2","0","2","1","-","2","0","2","2"," school"," year",".","\n\n","The"," OSP"," is"," administered"," by"," the"," DC"," Education"," Council"," on"," the"," Seamless"," Choice"," of"," High"," Quality"," Schools"," (","also"," known"," as"," the"," DC"," Scholarship"," Office","),"," an"," independent"," agency"," within"," the"," District"," of"," Columbia"," government","."," The"," agency"," is"," responsible"," for"," selecting"," scholarship"," recipients",","," providing"," program"," oversight",","," and"," monitoring"," participating"," schools",".","\n\n","To"," be"," eligible"," for"," the"," program",","," students"," must"," reside"," within"," the"," District"," of"," Columbia"," and"," come"," from"," families"," with"," incomes"," at"," or"," below"," ","1","8","5","%"," of"," the"," federal"," poverty"," level","."," Scholarships"," are"," awarded"," on"," a"," first","-","come",","," first","-","served"," basis"," and"," are"," worth"," up"," to"," $","1","2",",","6","7","9"," for"," elementary"," school"," students",","," $","1","8",",","7","2","3"," for"," middle"," school"," students",","," and"," $","2","5",",","5","2","4"," for"," high"," school"," students",".","\n\n","The"," program"," has"," been"," the"," subject"," of"," considerable"," debate",","," with"," supporters"," arguing"," that"," it"," provides"," low","-","income"," families"," with"," greater"," access"," to"," high","-","quality"," education"," and"," improves"," student"," outcomes",","," while"," critics"," contend"," that"," it"," diver","ts"," resources"," from"," the"," District"," of"," Columbia"," Public"," Schools"," and"," does"," not"," lead"," to"," significant"," academic"," gains",".","\n\n","According"," to"," a"," ","2","0","1","9"," evaluation"," by"," the"," U",".","S","."," Department"," of"," Education",","," students"," who"," used"," OSP"," scholarships"," were"," more"," likely"," to"," graduate"," from"," high"," school"," and"," attend"," college"," than"," their"," peers"," who"," did"," not"," use"," the"," scholarships","."," However",","," the"," report"," also"," found"," that"],"sub_source":"wikipedia","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}